---
title: Pork Chop Milanese with Penne
description: The iconic Italian-American dish we know and love is back, but this time in pork form! Savoury breaded pork chops smothered in a bright tomato sauce and sprinkled with just the right amount of mozzarella go perfectly with penne and fresh spinach!
